{"tid":42010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擊破五毛繆誤，想做個100毛投票","createTime":"2016-12-16T10:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T02:59:32.000Z","uid":65056,"like":84,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4d21edd82d7928c954a11051a48d83c2733d79","tid":42010,"uid":65056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:17:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我唔知呢到個主流意見係咪真係反100毛<br />\n<br />\n但又見到政事台d 撚樣成日拎住呢樣野黎講，所以想做個投票展示返真正民意<br />\n<br />\n利申：覺得個女仔冇做錯野都俾人恰睇唔過眼<br />\n<br />\n正評：對100毛冇意見或支持<br />\n負評：反100毛"},{"pid":"4396598f7716729884ff00fed1708f5ecef2617a","tid":42010,"uid":65056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人有興趣知道真相？"},{"pid":"02b2b7014c0c09c3a86cced4233fdbe1d79f821a","tid":42010,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"你個投票本身已經有問題"},{"pid":"37bd605ca900a719e78bb7bc42bcf211b0e82d72","tid":42010,"uid":65056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個投票本身已經有問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁唔一定要支持既，我自己純粹鐘意就睇下，唔係話好支持果種<br />\n<br />\n我見佢地話呢到好多人反所以想知究竟係唔係"},{"pid":"877d64908e42c274665b4d183a5aaac0f4a30329","tid":42010,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"個分類都幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be90ad0c2141c8b193deaad554b8c0b531201ac6","tid":42010,"uid":65056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個分類都幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我唔係想做bias<br />\n<br />\n不過如果個命題係「呢到主流意見係反100毛」，我覺得個分類都ok 呀<br />\n<br />\n有冇專業人士俾d意見可以點set 好 d"},{"pid":"37ddbec92a58ebc7acb5a5f51f51279ee11741fc","tid":42010,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"支持港版結衣"},{"pid":"ed0728b56e972f6f9dc85957ac7b866e71767550","tid":